metadata.name: One last time
metadata.description:
Collection: Secret Windows Editions

Artist: Ana Julia Gobbi

Edition: Limited to 30

There is nothing more striking in the black cube of the night than these rectangles of light. They flicker through the darkness, and in that moment, you are drawn into their world. You see things that are fragments of a long story, and you have no idea if what you see is a beginning, an end, or just that endless movement in between. It's a frightening but so familiar place that you run away from, and yet there it is again, on the other side of the glass.
